                <mxCell id="aiWsRoutes" value="WS /ingest/:broadcastId?classroomId=…&amp;sessionId=…&#xa;       ← binary PCM s16le 16 kHz mono (from Origin/FFmpeg)&#xa;       — Pipes audio to STT provider (Deepgram)&#xa;       — Chunks text · creates Transcript + TranscriptChunk&#xa;       — Embeds via sentence-transformers/OpenAI (384-d)&#xa;       — Publishes transcription:chunk on Redis" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#6E35E5;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fontSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
