                <mxCell id="socketOrigin" value="Origin Server Socket.IO (WebRTC signaling):&#xa;- getRouterRtpCapabilities&#xa;- createWebRtcTransport&#xa;- connectTransport&#xa;- startBroadcast / stopBroadcast&#xa;- joinBroadcast / consume&#xa;- transcription:control (start/stop)&#xa;- viewerCount" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#FF5722;align=left;spacingLeft=10;fontSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
